rows.label: qst201805_msg0003
rows.name: Let's go talk to them right away!

rows.label: qst201805_msg0004
rows.name:
Hold on! If we go empty-handed,
it'll be a repeat of last time.

rows.label: qst201805_msg0005
rows.name: Ah, you're right! We need souvenirs!

rows.label: qst201805_msg0006
rows.name:
...Then let's find out what
the Phonexes here like!

rows.label: qst201805_msg0007
rows.name:
We can't get Pinfins here, so their
favorite must be something else.
